{"title":"[数据结构]区间和","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1156#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=1156","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1156/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/1156/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/1156"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给定一个长为n的序列，接下来m次操作，每次操作会对序列某段区间内所有数加上一个值，或者询问一段区间的和，n,m(n<=100000,m<=500000)。\r\n\r\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入数据第一行包含两个正整数n,m(n<=100000,m<=500000),以下是m行，\r\n每行有三个正整数k,a,b(k=0或1, a,b<=n).k=0时表示将a处数字加上b,k=1时表示询问区间[a,b]内所有数的和。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于每个询问输出对应的答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"【输入样例】\r\n```\r\n10 20\r\n0 1 10\r\n1 1 4\r\n0 6 6\r\n1 4 10\r\n1 8 9\r\n1 4 9\r\n0 10 2\r\n1 1 8\r\n0 2 10\r\n1 3 9\r\n0 7 8\r\n0 3 10\r\n0 1 1\r\n1 3 8\r\n1 6 9\r\n0 5 5\r\n1 1 8\r\n0 4 2\r\n1 2 8\r\n0 1 1\r\n```\r\n【输出样例】\r\n```\r\n10\r\n6\r\n0\r\n6\r\n16\r\n6\r\n24\r\n14\r\n50\r\n41\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"n<=100000\r\n\r\nm<=500000"}]}